.help ovenr Oct mirror
.ih
NAME
ovenr -- Oven rotation speed reader.
.ih
USAGE
ovenr
.ih
PARAMETERS
.ls connection = oven0v0,5107
The host and port to connect to.
.le
.ls lower = 0
The lower speed limit.
.le
.ls upper = 0
The upper speed limit.
.le
.ih
DESCRIPTION
	Connect to the oven V computer and print on STDOUT the rotation speed
data.  Beep on STDERR if the speed is not between the limits.
.ih
EXAMPLES
	cl> ovenr connection="oven0v0,5107" > rspeed.oven0v0 &
.ih
BUGS
.ih
SEE ALSO
.endhelp
